Here’s some insight into how we’re keeping organised and on track with our projects.... we just love a good checklist and it’s become the very essence of our productivity. Want to give it a try?
.
Step 1. Get yourself this book - The Checklist Manifesto by Atul Gawande- for convincing evidence of how well the humble checklist works in a variety of industries (even surgeons), and just raw inspiration and interest.
.
Step 2. Grab yourself a beautiful checklist notepad from Muji.
.
Step 3. Use the Wunderlist app for... well, everything! It’ll take a bit of trial and error to refine your lists into what works for you but stick with it and make it your new habit. Productivity guaranteed 👌.
.
What are we missing fellow checklist enthusiasts?.
.

A huge project we’ve been working on for some time has come to completion and we are so proud of it! The Loherb Group is a company in Taiwan with several business entities under it, the most prominent being its beautiful Villa in picturesque Yilan on Taiwan’s East coast. We were tasked with giving Loherb a uniform identity across all of its businesses and building websites for each of them. We’ll post more about each of them individually in due course but for now here’s a taste of what we’ve been up to. At the tip of the iceberg this project included: .
✅ Redesign logos to bring unity across all divisions of the company
✅Give each business within company its own unique ‘visual language’ to be implemented in branding and websites
✅Design and create 4 stunning websites (plus a 5th parent website)
✅Elegantly write all English copy for websites to invoke character of product and services
✅Build an admin website to manage content for all sites in one place
✅Make each website dual language
✅Allow blog posts to be posted across the websites of their choosing
✅Facebook messenger integration across all sites
✅Instagram integration across all sites
✅Direct booking function integration on the Villa website
✅Clean, user-friendly and attractive design
✅Responsive
✅Happy client

These websites have been up for little over a month and are already garnering thousands of page views and causing much delight amongst Loherb’s clientele. 
It’s been a pleasure working with you @loherb0301 and we look forward to more!
